<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>RESULT</title>
    <style>
      span {
        color: coral;
        font-weight: 700;
      }
      .roundbox {
        border: 1px solid #ddd;
        border-radius: 5px;
        padding: 10px;
        margin-bottom: 10px;
        box-shadow: 2px 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <h1><%=title%>결과 확인하기</h1>
    <p><span><%=userInfo.name%></span>님 환영합니다</p>
    <p class="roundbox">성별 : <%=userInfo.gender%></p>
    <p class="roundbox">
      생년월일 : <%=userInfo.year%>/<%=userInfo.month%>/<%=userInfo.day%>
    </p>
    <p class="roundbox">관심사 : <%=userInfo.category%></p>

    <h3>다른 태그 작성해보기</h3>
    <p>좋아하는 색 : <%=userInfo.favcolor%></p>
    <p>이메일 : <%=userInfo.email%></p>

    <a href="/">홈으로 이동</a>
  </body>
</html>
